ownedComment.body: OntoUML is a UML Profile whose elements represent finer-grained distinctions between different kinds of types and encompasses a set of constraints defining the admissible relations between these elements. It is particularly suited for modeling domain ontologies.

J. Guerson, T. P. Sales, G. Guizzardi et al., OntoUML Lightweight Editor: A Model-Based Environment to Build, Evaluate and Implement Reference Ontologies, 2015 IEEE 19th International Enterprise Distributed Object Computing Workshop, pp. 144-147, 2015.

properties.documentation: NEMO (Ncleo de Estudos em Modelagem Conceitual e Ontologias) is a research group devoted to investigating the application of domain and foundational ontologies as well as ontology-based techniques in various aspects of conceptual modeling such as information modeling, enterprise modeling, agent-based systems and semantic web.

OntoUML is a UML Profile whose elements represent finer-grained distinctions between different kinds of types and encompasses a set of constraints defining the admissible relations between these elements. It is particularly suited for modeling domain ontologies.

J. Guerson, T. P. Sales, G. Guizzardi et al., OntoUML Lightweight Editor: A Model-Based Environment to Build, Evaluate and Implement Reference Ontologies, 2015 IEEE 19th International Enterprise Distributed Object Computing Workshop, pp. 144-147, 2015.

properties.alias: (Guizzardi G. 2005 Ontological Foundations for Structural Conceptual Models p.360)

properties.documentation: As administraes pblicas competentes exigem a elaborao e implantao de um Plano de Autoproteo aos titulares de atividades de negcios para obterem autorizao para funcionamento em suas respectivas instalaes .
Instalao - Centro, estabelecimento, espao ou dependencia a totalidade da zona sob controle de um titular onde se desenvolve uma atividade de negcio.

Documento com funes planejadas para uma atividade de negcio ou instalao com o objetivo de prevenir e controlar os riscos sobre as pessoas e bens e dar resposta adequada s possveis situaes de emergncias.
